# {{product}} forge

This directory is a **forge** for the product `{{product}}`.

- Workdir: `{{workdir}}`
- Memory:  `./memory/` (pull-synced from `{{s3_uri}}`)
- Master:  `.claude/agents/{{product}}-master.md`
- Profile: `./profile.yaml`

This directory is private. Do not commit it. Do not place any of its
contents into `{{workdir}}`. The product remains unaware of the forge.

## Two ways to use this forge

**In-session bind (default):**
From any Claude Code session, in any cwd, run `/forge {{product}}`.
The slash command pulls memory, loads the master persona, and adopts
it for the rest of the session.

**Launcher fallback:**
`cd` into this directory and run `claude`. The project-level
`.claude/settings.json` here grants workdir permissions and runs a
SessionStart memory sync. The master agent is still a `taa`-discovered
persona; this directory does not redefine sub-agents.

## What may not happen here

- No sub-agent definitions. Sub-agents are `taa` journeymen.
- No writes into `{{workdir}}` without explicit user approval per change.
- No commits of this directory anywhere.

See `ta-set/taf/ETHOS.md` for the full forge concept.
